as your's have made you.

Pho! don't tell me of angelic ſweetneſs;

a young fellow ſhould be content with nothing leſs

than mortal ſweetneſs, when with a blooming girl.

Tranſporting hour! And wilt thou yet

be Henry's? Oh bind the promiſe on thy knee;

—invoke the ſacred powers to witneſs it.

entering No, Sir,—I am the arbiter of

